OL,6,F"Discrepancies don't come from
OL,7,Fdishonesty but from dysfunction,"
OL,8,FAdvocate Herold-Howes told the Court.
OL,10,FBut after four and a half hours of
OL,11,Fdeliberation on Tuesday, the jury
OL,12,Ffound Mitten guilty on all three of
OL,13,Fthe counts he faced.
OL,15,FCommissioner Andrew Oldland,
OL,16,Fpresiding, told Mitton that he will be
OL,17,Fremanded in custody and return to the
OL,18,FRoyal Court at a later date for
OL,19,Fsentencing.
