OL,6,FDetective Constable Shaun Smith, who
OL,7,Fled the investigation for the States
OL,8,Fof Jersey Police, said: "Mr Mitton was
OL,9,Fa trusted employee at Hunt Bros
OL,10,FLimited, a family-run business that
OL,11,Fplaced immense faith in its staff.
OL,13,F"The betrayal of this trust by Mr
OL,14,FMitton, who exploited his position for
OL,15,Fpersonal gain, was deeply troubling
OL,16,Ffor the family."
